precentacion: Hello my name is Eduardo and I am a full stack developer,
about.description.1: I am a full-stack developer passionate about technology and experienced in a wide range of JavaScript frameworks and compilers such as Angular, React, TypeScript, Node.js and jQuery. I love experimenting with new technologies and learning how they can be used to create innovative and efficient solutions.
about.description.2: In my last project, I developed a web application to assist in the work of a family member, using Angular and Node.js. The application automated tasks such as records management and report generation, which allowed him to increase his productivity by 20% and reduce the time spent on records management by 50%. I also have experience in creating RESTful APIs, optimizing web application performance and developing backends with Node.js and MySQL.
about.description.3: In the development of these applications I have focused on creating intuitive and easy to use interfaces, putting into practice my knowledge in UI/UX design. In addition to my front-end experience, I also have experience in backend development and database management. I am a hard worker, responsible and team player. I am confident that my skills and experience can be of great value to your company and I am excited for the opportunity to contribute to your success.
